-- Masco Reaches Settlement in Insulation Price-Fixing Case
-- B y   D a v i d   B e a s l e y
-- 2012-08-01T13:12:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-01/masco-reaches-settlement-in-insulation-price-fixing-case.html
Masco Corp. (MAS)  reached a settlement of
claims by independent contractors that it colluded with
insulation makers to fix prices, according to a court filing.
The judge in the case gave the parties until Aug. 17 to file the
proposed settlement in federal court in Atlanta.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
